Name: UTM GRID ZONE
Explanation: ONE OF THE 60 LONGITUDINAL PROJECTION ZONES IN THE UTM GRID, NUMBERED 1 TO 60 STARTING AT 180°W.

Name: MGRS (UTM) GRID LATITUDE BAND
Explanation: ONE OF THE 20 LATITUDINAL ZONES OF THE MGRS (UTM) GRID SPANNING THE LATITUDES 80°S TO 84°N.

Name: MGRS (UTM) 100KM BOX
Explanation: LETTER PAIR DESIGNATING ONE OF THE 100,000 METRE GRID SQUARES WITHIN A UTM GRID ZONE.
